Mempelajari minda manusia,

00:16:21.680 --> 00:16:23.480
memanipulasi hati orang,

00:16:23.560 --> 00:16:25.320
kadang-kadang ia agak menarik,

00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:26.120
bukan?

